Command
---------------------------------------------------
python message.py youruserlist.txt yourxmlfile.xml --send_email



youruserlist.txt Composition
---------------------------------------------------
username email
ex:
Ricardo ricardo@gmail.com
Diogo diogo@hotmail.com

message.py
---------------------------------------------------
Email server is hardcoded to gmail
Need to change your sender email and respective password
You can also change the subject and message of the email, all of this in the writeEmail
This script won't add duplicate usernames to the XML

NOTE: Remove the "--send_email" flag if you do not want to send emails. 


IMPORTANT: you may need to change the permissions of your sender email to allow access to less safe aplications
